    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm a little confused with this, if this was straight from the-- from Lager I.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I'm positive that I was back, they took back.",
